# MorphixAI API Key for integration tests
#
# Setup:
#   1. Visit https://baibian.app/api-keys to create an API Key (select ALL scopes)
#   2. Copy the key below
#   3. Visit https://baibian.app/connections to link your third-party accounts
#      (GitHub, GitLab, Jira, Outlook, MS To Do, Notion, Confluence, etc.)
#   4. Run tests: npx vitest run test/app-clients/
#
MORPHIXAI_API_KEY=mk_your_api_key_here
